 defines a helper function `get_divisors` that calculates the divisors of a number and checks if there are exactly four divisors. If there are exactly four divisors, it returns the set of divisors; otherwise, it returns `None`. The main function iterates over the input list `nums`, uses the helper function to check each number, and sums the divisors of numbers that have exactly four divisors.", "estimated_date": 1584835200000}